除了会员、赞助商、期刊和出版商在它们的工作流程或数据库中包含ORCID，其他服务也可以这样做。范例：{{tsl|en|Journal of Neuroscience|神经科学杂志}}<ref name="JoN"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.jneurosci.org/site/misc/announcementspage.xhtml "Announcements"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jneurosci.org/site/misc/announcementspage.xhtml |date=20140622104524 }}. </cite></ref><ref name="SfNeuroscience"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.sfn.org/news-and-calendar/news-and-calendar/news/spotlight/2014/the-journal-of-neuroscience-rolls-out-orcid-integration "The Journal of Neuroscience Rolls Out ORCID Integration"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sfn.org/news-and-calendar/news-and-calendar/news/spotlight/2014/the-journal-of-neuroscience-rolls-out-orcid-integration |date=20140421052526 }}. </cite></ref>、[[施普林格出版社|施普林格出版社]]<ref name="SpringerPub"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.springer.com/authors/author+zone?SGWID=0-168002-12-1028464-0 "Author Zone 16 - ORCID"]{{Dead link}}. </cite></ref>、{{tsl|en|Hindawi Publishing Corporation|辛迪维出版公司}}<ref name="Asakura"><cite class="citation web">[https://www.hindawi.com/80647648/ "Hiroshi Asakura"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.hindawi.com/80647648/ |date=20180612143004 }}. </cite></ref>、{{tsl|en|Europe PubMed Central|欧洲PubMed中心}}<ref name="EPMC"><cite class="citation web">[http://europepmc.org/orcid/import "ORCID Article Claiming"] {{Wayback|url=http://europepmc.org/orcid/import |date=20140917092545 }}. </cite></ref>、日本{{tsl|en|国家信息学研究所}}的研究员名称解析器<ref name="Resolver"><cite class="citation web">[http://rns.nii.ac.jp/html_us/orcid_integration_help_en.html "ORCID integration"] {{Wayback|url=http://rns.nii.ac.jp/html_us/orcid_integration_help_en.html |date=20140421064132 }}. </cite></ref>，以及[[维基百科|维基百科]]<ref name="Wikipedia"><cite class="citation web">Wikipedia authors. </cite></ref>、[[维基数据|维基数据]]等也都有使用<ref name="Wikidata"><cite class="citation web">Wikidata contributors. </cite></ref>。

一些服务已经创建了工具来导出到或导入自ORCID。这包括[[斯高帕斯数据库|斯高帕斯数据库]]<ref name="Scopus"><cite class="citation web">[http://orcid.scopusfeedback.com "Scopus2Orcid - Use the Scopus to Orcid Author details and documents wizard to collect all your Scopus records in one unique author profile"] {{Wayback|url=http://orcid.scopusfeedback.com/ |date=20140724124524 }}. </cite></ref>、{{tsl|en|Figshare}}<ref name="Figshare"><cite class="citation web">[http://figshare.com/blog/figshare_ORCID_integration/86 "figshare ORCID integration"] {{Wayback|url=http://figshare.com/blog/figshare_ORCID_integration/86 |date=20140531205950 }}. </cite></ref>、Thomson Reuters的[[ResearcherID|ResearcherID]]系统<ref name="ResearcherID"><cite class="citation web">[http://wokinfo.com/researcherid/integration/ "RID - ORCID Integration - IP & Science"] {{Wayback|url=http://wokinfo.com/researcherid/integration/ |date=20150912140531 }}. </cite></ref>、{{tsl|en|Researchfish}}<ref name="Researchfish"><cite class="citation web">[https://www.researchfish.com/node/2525 "Researchfish now integrating with the ORCID registry"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.researchfish.com/node/2525 |date=20150715022313 }}. </cite></ref>、[[大英图书馆|大英图书馆]]（为其[[EThOS|EThOS]]论文目录）<ref name="EThOS"><cite class="citation web">[http://ethos.bl.uk/About.do "British Library EThOS - about searching and ordering theses online"] {{Wayback|url=http://ethos.bl.uk/About.do |date=20160321162734 }}. </cite></ref>、[[ProQuest|ProQuest]]（为其{{tsl|en|ProQuest Dissertations and Theses}}服务）<ref name="ProQuest"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.proquest.com/blog/pqblog/2015/Connected-from-the-Beginning-Adding-ORCID-to-ETDs.html "Connected from the Beginning: Adding ORCID to ETDs"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.proquest.com/blog/pqblog/2015/Connected-from-the-Beginning-Adding-ORCID-to-ETDs.html |date=20151225075056 }}. </cite></ref>以及{{tsl|en|Frontiers Media#Loop|Frontiers Loop}}<ref><cite class="citation web">Ponto, Michelle (7 October 2015). </cite></ref>。
